## Key Discussion Points

### 1. Introduction and Administration
Arndt Rogge opened the meeting, highlighting the tight one-hour agenda. The chairs presented the [Chairs' slides](https://datatracker.ietf.org/meeting/126/materials/slides-126-sml-chairs-slides-00) and noted the agenda breakdown.

